## API Reference

### Message Protocol

All messages are JSON-formatted and follow this structure:

```json
{
  "type": "message_type",
  "data": {},
  "timestamp": "ISO-8601 timestamp"
}
```

### Client → Server Messages

#### Route Request
```json
{
  "type": "route",
  "query": "Your query here"
}
```

#### Statistics Request
```json
{
  "type": "stats"
}
```

#### Ping
```json
{
  "type": "ping"
}
```

### Server → Client Messages

#### Connection Acknowledgment
```json
{
  "type": "connection",
  "status": "connected",
  "stats": {...},
  "timestamp": "2025-01-11T10:30:00"
}
```

#### Routing Result
```json
{
  "type": "routing_result",
  "result": "gpt-4",
  "query": "Your query",
  "timestamp": "2025-01-11T10:30:01"
}
```

See [WEBSOCKET_SERVER.md](WEBSOCKET_SERVER.md) for complete API documentation.

